videos.description: Kevin Durant runs into Giannis Antetokounmpo after a Nets basket and later on KD shoves Giannis to the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Things get chippy between Giannis and KD early on) 2021/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Things get chippy between Giannis and KD early on

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo flies to the bucket for a powerful one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis fired up after dunk) 2021/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis fired up after dunk

videos.description: James Harden lofts the ball near the basket to Kevin Durant, who finishes with a one-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden perfectly places pass to KD for dunk) 2021/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden perfectly places pass to KD for dunk

videos.description: James Harden saves the ball from going out of bounds by bouncing it between Brook Lopez's legs, which has him a little scared.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden's incredible save spooks Lopez) 2021/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden's incredible save spooks Lopez

videos.description: After the Nets snag an offensive rebound, James Harden kicks it out to Kevin Durant, who drains a go-ahead 3-pointer with 36.3 seconds left in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant comes up clutch on go-ahead 3-pointer) 2021/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant comes up clutch on go-ahead 3-pointer

videos.description: Kevin Durant and James Harden combine for 64 points, with KD hitting the go-ahead 3-pointer late in the Nets' 125-123 win vs. the Bucks.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Durant, Harden lead Nets in thrilling win vs. Bucks) 2021/01/18 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Durant, Harden lead Nets in thrilling win vs. Bucks

videos.description: Down 125-123 in the final seconds, Khris Middleton puts up a 3-pointer and it goes in and out, as the Bucks fall to the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Middleton in and out on game winner) 2021/1/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Middleton in and out on potential game winner

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo rebounds the Jrue Holiday missed layup with a tip-in dunk.
